name: ADJ01WorldSettings
doc: The default world settings object, used primarily to set the default gameplay experience to use when playing on this map

DefaultGameplayExperience: The default experience to use when a server opens this map if it is not overridden by the user-facing experience
ForceStandaloneNetMode:
Is this level part of a front-end or other standalone experience?
When set, the net mode will be forced to Standalone when you hit Play in the editor
